subject: Re:     Mrs Bekky Johnson.
body:
Hello Mrs. Becky Johnson,

Thank you for your detailed message. I appreciate the effort you and Mr. John Barnes have put into ensuring the smooth delivery of my package.

I'm a bit confused about the options you've provided for delivery, though. Could you please clarify what each option entails? Specifically, I'd like to understand what the differences are between them in terms of delivery speed, courier charges, and insurance coverage.

Also, could you provide more information about how the tracking system works? I've never used a tracking number before and would like to know how it can help me keep tabs on my package.

Looking forward to your response!

Best wishes,
Ida
